item.description: Our group always draws a big crowd for dancing on Fridays so let's try an old standby, Princeton Station. Rock City band will be playing...if anyone knows or has heard them post a comment if you wish, otherwise let's just head over and have some fun. Always good laughs and nice people when we get together.
item.how_to_find_us: Reply if you plan to arrive by 7:30 for dinner and help gather tables..no reservations here in the lounge....we'll be the folks "hovering" LOL! and we all look like our pics!
